title: Pregnancy Top 7 & All About Spinning
description:
Jillian is joined by Dr. Katja van Herle (board certified UCLA endocrinologist) with her Top 7 things to do in planning to get pregnant.  Then it's call time and Jillian gets down to some awesome guidance when tackling a spinning class.
